Listen announces on the local transport address.

```ts
const listener1 = Deno.listenDatagram({
  port: 80,
  transport: "udp"
});
const listener2 = Deno.listenDatagram({
  hostname: "golang.org",
  port: 80,
  transport: "udp"
});
```

Requires `allow-net` permission.

